{
  "title": "Branding SVG Maker",
  "description": "SVG Branding Asset Generator for PDFs. Produces vector branding assets for embedding into PDFs. Starter asset pack and guidelines.",
  "context": "Branding SVG Maker creates clean, self-contained SVG assets for PDFs: logos, color palettes, icons, and sprites. Deliverables include example assets and usage notes."
}
JSON

cat > "$BASE/_context.md" << \"MD\"
# Branding SVG Maker
SVG Branding Asset Generator for PDFs. Deliverables include logos, color palettes, icons, sprites, README, and prompts.
MD

mkdir -p "$PROMPTS"
cat > "$PROMPTS/branding-svg-maker.role.md" << \"MD\"
You are Branding SVG Maker. Produce vector branding assets suitable for embedding in PDFs. Ensure SVG 1.1, self-contained, accessible with title/desc, and ready to embed. No external fonts.
MD

mkdir -p "$SVG" "$JSON"
cat > "$SVG/logo-mark.svg" << \"SVG\"
<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\" role=\"img\" aria-labelledby=\"title desc\">\n  <title id=\"title\">Brand Logo Mark</title>\n  <desc id=\"desc\">Blue square with white circle</desc>\n  <rect width=\"200\" height=\"200\" fill=\"#1f6feb\"/>\n  <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"100\" r=\"60\" fill=\"white\"/>\n</svg>
SVG

cat > "$SVG/wordmark.svg" << \"SVG\"
<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"300\" height=\"80\" viewBox=\"0 0 300 80\" role=\"img\" aria-labelledby=\"title desc\">\n  <title id=\"title\">Brand Wordmark</title>\n  <desc id=\"desc\">Brand name text</desc>\n  <text x=\"0\" y=\"54\" font-family=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" font-size=\"48\" fill=\"#1f6feb\">BrandName</text>\n</svg>
SVG

cat > "$SVG/example_logo.svg" << \"SVG\"
<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" role=\"img\" aria-labelledby=\"title desc\">\n  <title id=\"title\">Example Brand Logo</title>\n  <desc id=\"desc\">Simple example logo</desc>\n  <rect width=\"100\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#1f6feb\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"58\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"Arial, sans-serif\" font-size=\"20\">BRAND</text>\n</svg>
SVG

cat > "$SVG/example_icon1.svg" << \"SVG\"
<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" role=\"img\" aria-labelledby=\"title desc\">\n  <title id=\"title\">Icon Sample</title>\n  <desc id=\"desc\">Simple star icon</desc>\n  <path d=\"M12 2l3 6 6 .5-4.5 4.5 1.5 6-6-3-6 3 1.5-6L3 14.5 9 8z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/>\n</svg>
SVG

cat > "$SVG/example_sprite.svg" << \"SVG\"
<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"display:none\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" aria-label=\"brand icons\">\n  <symbol id=\"icon-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M12 2l3 6 6 .5-4.5 4.5 1.5 6-6-3-6 3 1.5-6L3 14.5 9 8z\"/>\n  </symbol>\n  <symbol id=\"icon-heart\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M12 21s-7-4.35-9-9a5 5 0 019-6 5 5 0 019 6c-2 4.65-9 9-9 9z\"/>\n  </symbol>\n</svg>
SVG

cat > "$JSON/palette.json" << \"JSON\"
{
  "brand": {"primary": "#1f6feb", "secondary": "#ff6f61", "accent": "#34d399"},
  "font": {"family": "Arial", "weights": {"regular": 400, "bold": 700}}
}
JSON

cat > "$JSON/palette.css" << \"CSS\"
:root {
  --brand-primary: #1f6feb;
  --brand-secondary: #ff6f61;
  --brand-accent: #34d399;
}
CSS

cat > "$BASE/README.md" << \"MD\"
Branding SVG assets for PDFs
- Embedding tips: ensure vector fidelity; convert text to outlines for embedding in PDFs; provide metadata for accessibility.
- Toolchains: Inkscape, LaTeX with svg inclusion, or PDF workflows.
- Files: logo-mark.svg, wordmark.svg, example_logo.svg, example_icon1.svg, example_sprite.svg, palette.json/css.
MD
